data.description: Priced well for a quick sale! Unusual find in Villa Maria. House is only 5.5 years old and sits on .52 acres. New 20x30 wooden covered deck provides a relaxing place for the family as well as to entertain guests. The house is all electric but there is natural gas in the neighborhood. Seller is providing a home warranty for a Buyer. This home is very close to the hospital, library, schools, doctors' offices and restaurants. Access to I-10 is less than 5 minutes! Schedule your showing today!
